{"tid":1446649,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林奠冇講錯 你地no stake in the society","createTime":"2019-08-11T15:10:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T15:13:39.000Z","uid":78146,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ad4a11f079a74573219c13fcd138a8bd425d99b4","tid":1446649,"uid":78146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:10:49.000Z","msg":"睇埋先屌<br />\n<br />\n今次嘅反送中運動 點解我地可以引起咁大嘅回響？ 因為我地冇大台 冇路可捉 我地用新時代嘅媒體 起了一場政治革命 <br />\n<br />\n然而<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">冇大台係我地嘅弱點</span></strong> 運動開初我地有清晰的目標 有清晰嘅訴求 但我今日係前線係見到迷惘 <br />\n<br />\n一班人著住裝備 <span style=\"color: red;\">如同學生班會旅行討論</span>點做 難道咁討論法有結果？你知道係人定係鬼？<br />\n<br />\n依場運動已經去到一個樽頸位 我地已經流失緊民意 流失緊主流嘅支（此處不敍）<span style=\"color: red;\">我地要諗：點樣可以保住我地嘅political power</span><br />\n<br />\n冇大台 有利有弊 我地分散得黎又集中 信息傳遞快 我地包容亦團結對外 <span style=\"color: red;\">But</span>:We are nobody 我地匿名 係實體亦只能匿名 我地political power備受限制 一般市民見到嘅 可以係義士 亦可以係暴徒 <span style=\"color: blue;\">所以我地要轉型</span>將我地今日嘅力量轉移去現實社會 <span style=\"color: red;\">唔再係no stake in the society</span><br />\n<br />\n首先 <span style=\"color: red;\">我地要將「新時代力量」轉到實體政治</span> 點解政治要專門劃分？點解有政客出現？因為佢地有政治智慧 識玩政治手段 佢地嘅職業係「政治從業員」而我地只不過係業餘 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">我地要代理人</span>各大網絡溝道依然係主要平台 民間記者會係我地嘅口舌 但<span style=\"color: red;\">泛民會係我地浮上政治夢台的代理人</span> 大家或者唔係泛民嘅支持者 亦未必認同佢地嘅理念 <span style=\"color: red;\">但政客比我地更會政治</span> 我地同泛民應該互相利用 同時 避免被騎劫 以建立equalise嘅政治體為目標 <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">成為建制、泛民以外嘅Third party</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n目前 我地要重整旗鼓 清點得著 同時修補網上力量嘅漏洞 <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>暫時停止所以活動 訂立deadline 民間記者會邀請泛民 利用泛民係制度爭取 當泛民談判失敗後重上場</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n我地唔係做泛民嘅旗子 <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">係互相利用 令我地have stake in  political and society</span></strong></span> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">咁先係真正嘅：光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"c564f2aad3247c8bb507339c687e75af492f115a","tid":1446649,"uid":78146,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:11:52.000Z","msg":"自推10連"},{"pid":"b9c60c9b75f6a1bbb569d8b00fe38dec7dc80be1","tid":1446649,"uid":78146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:12:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e0b7a8f6ed2db21b0567c7ac6e5ed33026c0b1ef","tid":1446649,"uid":78146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:12:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"231fa85b6437bf27390ec8f64ad0bca76761818f","tid":1446649,"uid":78146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:12:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"09677d5e8bf8e7ca9c2a9dbe156c73bda7bd434e","tid":1446649,"uid":78146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:12:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bc696b6cb9e937ed381ddc98dc75067d80b7ed24","tid":1446649,"uid":78146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:12:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8c3de1c1e23a2a089824fc79ad9f292e85a1f299","tid":1446649,"uid":78146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:13:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"30151b124260d12be344ec007c1fcf4e97667492","tid":1446649,"uid":78146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:13:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c747475499f72d361dcb1743f7760fcd1635e365","tid":1446649,"uid":78146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:13:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3149218afa7a367876a359f83cc56d109f437ec5","tid":1446649,"uid":78146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:13:39.000Z","msg":"推"}]}